SEO Bootcamp Part 4

Don’t let common Shopify mistakes hold your business back 🚫

🔑 Tips

✨ Duplicate Content: Google doesn’t like clones! Use canonical tags to avoid penalties
✨ Slow Page Speed: Optimize images, leverage browser caching, and minify files
✨ Mobile Optimization: Ensure your store is mobile-friendly for better rankings
✨ Lack of Schema Markup: Help Google understand your content with rich snippets
